@startuml View Profile API Sequence
title View Profile API - Sequence Diagram

actor Client
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Auth Service" as Auth
participant "User Service" as US
database "User DB" as DB

Client -> GW: GET /api/users/{userId}
activate GW

GW -> Auth: Validate Token
activate Auth
Auth -> Auth: Extract JWT & Verify Signature
Auth --> GW: Token Valid
deactivate Auth

GW -> US: Get User Profile (userId)
activate US

US -> DB: Query User (userId)
activate DB
DB --> US: User Record
deactivate DB

US -> US: Format Response\n(sanitize fields)
US --> GW: User Profile JSON
deactivate US

GW --> Client: 200 OK\n{\n  "id": "user123",\n  "name": "John Doe",\n  "email": "john@example.com",\n  "joinDate": "2024-01-15"\n}
deactivate GW

@enduml
